üîß How to Get YouTube Playlist IDs:
Go to any YouTube playlist
Copy the URL - it looks like: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLrAl6rYGS6d7VGYfhOwMeFENcUKKVPLEY
Extract the ID - everything after list= (e.g., PLrAl6rYGS6d7VGYfhOwMeFENcUKKVPLEY)
Add to your JSON using the youtube_playlist_id field
üéµ Usage Options:
Option 1: Use youtube_playlist_id only - fetches all videos from that YouTube playlist
Option 2: Use videos array only - specify individual video IDs
Option 3: Use both - YouTube playlist + additional custom videos
